string:
In the meeting
room of a record
company…
Producer One is
reporting the
results of an
audition tape
made by a band
called the
Indies.

name: Mr.One
string:
We heard your
songs.
<name:37>Thank you very
much.
<name:32>About the result
… Mr. Meow, we
decided to hire
only you.
<name:34>Wait a minute!
I've been making
music with him
from the start.
There is no way
you can hire
only one of us!

<name:33>… … … …

<name:32>Well, it's all
up to you. Our
decision will
not change.

string:
<noname><name:34>Darn!!
<name:33>Good for you…
<name:34>What are you
saying!? We've
been together…

<name:33>It's your dream!
You always
wanted to become
famous and sing
in front of
large audiences
all around the
world!
<name:34>But…
<name:33>I've been just
holding you up…
You're a star
and I've always
been jealous. My
guitar playing
is no good,
but you are
different.
You will be big
someday! Don't
worry about me.
Take their
offer…
<name:32>… … … …
<name:34>…Alright,
Polo…

<noname><name:32>Mr. Meow. What
do you think?
<name:34>…Yes. I…
will do it!
<name:32>Good. I'm glad
to hear that.

name: Mr.One
string:
OK. Now the two
of you have to
try even harder
to make good
music!

name: Meow
string:
<name:34>What!? You
mean…?
<name:32>Yes. It was our
company's
decision to
hire both of
you!!

<name:37>Thank you very
much!!

<noname><name:32>“It's your
dreams!”…
Those kids…
They're just
like me when I
was younger…
They will make
their dreams
come true…
unlike me…
someday…
